### Avoid nesting output emit

When triggering the output emit, do not nest it in another function if there is no other action to perform.

```ts
// ✅ Good
@Component({
  // ...
  template: ` <button (click)="save.emit()">Save</button> `,
})
export class MyComponent {
  save = output();
}
```

